@SignalRadio.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5210

###
# Health Check
GET {{SignalRadio.Api_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###
# Upload Recording (WAV only)
POST {{SignalRadio.Api_HostAddress}}/api/recording/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="TalkgroupId"

12345
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Frequency"

851.0125
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="Timestamp"

2025-08-16T21:00:00Z
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="SystemName"

TestSystem
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="audioFile"; filename="sample.wav"
Content-Type: audio/wav

< ../../test-files/sample.wav
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

